Add the directory fonts to your TEXFONTS environmental variable.
export TEXFONTS=${TEXFONTS}:`pwd`/fonts

Add the directory texmf to your TEXINPUTS environmental variable.
export TEXINPUTS=${TEXINPUTS}:`pwd`/texmf

How to use tamiltrans?

1. Create a .ttex input file as shown in doc/tamiltransdoc.pdf
2. tamiltrans --help
3. tamiltrans < input.ttex > output.tex
4. latex output.tex
